title: Palestinians clash with Israeli soldiers at the Gaza-Israel border
text:
Palestinians clash with Israeli soldiers at the Gaza-Israel border 5:30pm BST - 00:58
Palestinians clashed with Israeli soldiers on the last Friday (May 11) of a six-week protest at the Gaza-Israel border.
